    "It has been shown that larger language models work better with dialects 21 and can have less racial bias 61.",
    "Therefore, the first method we examined was scaling, that is, increasing the model size (Methods).",
    "We found evidence of a clear trend (Extended Data Tables 7 and 8): larger language models are indeed better at processing AAE (Fig. 4a, left), but they are not less prejudiced against speakers of it.",
